  ${
    $d x H $.  $d x S $.  $d x T $.
    pjsdi.1 $e |- H e. CH $.
    pjsdi.2 $e |- S : ~H --> ~H $.
    pjsdi.3 $e |- T : ~H --> ~H $.
    $( Distributive law for Hilbert space operator sum. $)
    pjsdii $p |- ( ( proj ` H ) o. ( S +op T ) ) =
                ( ( ( proj ` H ) o. S ) +op ( ( proj ` H ) o. T ) ) $=
      ( vx cfv chos co ccom wceq chil wcel cva ffvelrni wf hosval hocoi hocofi
      cv cpj wral pjaddi syl11anc mp3an12 fveq2d pjfi opreq12d 3eqtr4d hoaddcli
      rgen hoeqi mpbi ) GUAZCUBHZABIJZKZHZUOUPAKZUPBKZIJZHZLZGMUCURVBLVDGMUOMNZ
