  ${
    pjsdi2.1 $e |- H e. CH $.
    pjsdi2.2 $e |- R : ~H --> ~H $.
    pjsdi2.3 $e |- S : ~H --> ~H $.
    pjsdi2.4 $e |- T : ~H --> ~H $.
    $( Chained distributive law for Hilbert space operator difference. $)
    pjsdi2i $p |- ( ( R o. ( S +op T ) ) =
                ( ( R o. S ) +op ( R o. T ) ) ->
           ( ( ( proj ` H ) o. R ) o. ( S +op T ) ) =
     ( ( ( ( proj ` H ) o. R ) o. S ) +op ( ( ( proj ` H ) o. R ) o. T ) ) ) $=
      ( chos co ccom wceq cpj cfv coeq2 hocofi pjsdii syl6eq coass opreq12i
      3eqtr4g ) ABCIJZKZABKZACKZIJZLZDMNZUCKZUHUDKZUHUEKZIJZUHAKZUBKUMBKZUMCKZI
      JUGUIUHUFKULUCUFUHOUDUEDEABFGPACFHPQRUHAUBSUNUJUOUKIUHABSUHACSTUA $.
      $( [30-Nov-2000] $)
